webPageReport.html:
Radiology - Overview   Radiology includes both diagnostic imaging (x-ray, CT, MRI, ultrasound) and therapeutic treatment (nuclear medicine, radiation oncology).

Cost savings opportunities:
• “High Tech” service utilization should be reviewed closely as these are very expensive (CT, MRI, PET)
• Cost effective, in-network providers or the use of pre-certification may be considered when utilization is significantly greater than benchmark

filter.Query:
SELECT TOP 100 USING OUTER JOIN [Local Plan Market Detail.Local Plan Market Short Description] 'COL1', 
((([Eligibility Global Date: Sum: Member Months] where [Group Detail.Business Line Code]='CP' AND [Plan Detail.Plan Type Code]='M' AND [dim_time_day.Reporting Period]='Current' ) 
/ 
( DateDiff(Month,(DateTime('V{CStartDate}')),(DateTime('V{CEndDate}')))  + 1 )))'COL0' ,  
[Local Plan Market Detail.Local Plan Market Code] 'COL2' 
FROM [ALL] 
DISPLAY WHERE ( ( [COL0]>=500 ) ) 
DISPLAY BY [COL0] DESC
